<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Verify Your Email - Sqaleshop</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h1 style="color: #000;">Verify Your Email</h1>
    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>Thanks for signing up for Sqaleshop! Please verify your email address by clicking the button below.</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{verificationLink}}" 
         style="background-color: #000; color: #fff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;">
        Verify Email Address
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <p>If you didn't create an account with us, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The Sqaleshop Team</p>
    
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0;">
    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 12px;">
      If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
      {{verificationLink}}
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 